kpi.name: M386B2C4

kpi_info.title: Long successful setups when the setup time is over the time defined by PRFILE.
kpi_info.use: Number of long successful setups when the setup time is over the time defined by the PRFILE parameter. The counter is updated when the signalling phase ends, that is before sending the ALERT message.

kpi.kpi_alias: Long successful setups when the setup time is over the time defined by PRFILE.
